---
export const prerender = true;

import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../../lib/constants';
---

<PageLayout title={`Design Experiments â€” ${SITE.name}`}>
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white dark:bg-slate-950">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400 text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Layout Experiments
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-display font-extrabold text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          Design Exploration
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Dva razlicita pristupa redizajnu sajta. Svaki ima svoju pocetnu stranicu i blog. Uporedi i odaberi koji ti se vise svidja.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Fireship Style Card -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <!-- Preview header -->
          <div class="relative h-48 overflow-hidden" style="background: #0a0a0a;">
            <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(255,110,0,0.15), transparent);"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center" style="background: #ff6e00;">
                    <span class="text-black font-black text-sm">N</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="font-bold text-white text-lg">nativefirst</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm font-mono" style="color: #888;">// dark &middot; bold &middot; dev-focused</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
              Fireship Style
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">
              Taman, minimalisan dizajn inspirisan Fireship.io. Crna pozadina, neon akcenti (narandzasta, plava, zelena), monospace font elementi, grid pozadina, code snippet u hero sekciji. Developer-first estetika.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500 space-y-1 mb-6">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span style="color: #ff6e00;">&#9679;</span> Crna pozadina sa grid patternima
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span style="color: #00b0ff;">&#9679;</span> Neon boje: narandzasta, plava, pink, zelena
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span style="color: #00e676;">&#9679;</span> Monospace tipografija za akcenat
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span style="color: #ffd600;">&#9679;</span> Code snippet u hero sekciji
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span style="color: #ff4081;">&#9679;</span> Kompaktan, info-gusti layout
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <a href="/experiment/fireship/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold text-black" style="background: #ff6e00;">
                Homepage
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
              </a>
              <a href="/experiment/fireship/blog" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:border-slate-400">
                Blog
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Josh Comeau Style Card -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <!-- Preview header -->
          <div class="relative h-48 overflow-hidden" style="background: #f9f5f0;">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b9d, #ff8a5c, #ffc764, #25c685, #4c9aff, #b37aff);"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(108,99,255,0.08), transparent);"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b9d, #ff8a5c, #ffc764, #25c685, #4c9aff, #b37aff);">
                    <span class="text-white font-black text-sm">NF</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="font-display font-bold text-lg" style="color: #1b2d45;">NativeFirst</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #617d98;">playful &middot; colorful &middot; interactive</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b9d, #ff8a5c, #ffc764, #25c685, #4c9aff, #b37aff);"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
              Josh Comeau Style
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">
              Topao, razigran dizajn inspirisan joshwcomeau.com. Svetla pozadina sa kremastim tonovima, rainbow gradijenti, kartice sa dubinom i senkama, zaobljeni elementi, plutajuce dekoracije. Prijatan i pristupacen.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500 space-y-1 mb-6">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span style="color: #ff6b9d;">&#9679;</span> Topla kremasta pozadina (#f9f5f0)
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span style="color: #4c9aff;">&#9679;</span> Rainbow gradient akcenti svuda
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span style="color: #25c685;">&#9679;</span> Bouncy animacije (cubic-bezier spring)
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span style="color: #ffc764;">&#9679;</span> Kartice sa viseslojnim senkama
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span style="color: #b37aff;">&#9679;</span> Plutajuci dekorativni elementi
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <a href="/experiment/comeau/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold text-white" style="background: #6c63ff;">
                Homepage
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
              </a>
              <a href="/experiment/comeau/blog" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:border-slate-400">
                Blog
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Comparison note -->
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500">
          Obe varijante koriste iste podatke (apps, blog postovi, engagement). Razlika je samo u vizuelnom pristupu.
          <br/>Svaka varijanta ima svoju navigaciju i footer prilagodjen stilu.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
